Once the flags are established, I extract the hour and minute components from the timestamps to determine which trading window applies—morning session between 07:45 and 09:45, or afternoon session between 14:45 and 16:45 UTC. Then I identify crossover and crossunder signals by comparing current and prior bar prices against the calculated midpoint levels.

